{% comment %}
  Custom template for the four Shopify policy pages
  (Shipping / Refund / Terms of Service / Privacy).

  The .liquid form is used here instead of policies.json because some
  Shopify policy renderers bypass JSON section templates. Both new
  sections fall back to policy.title / policy.body when
  request.page_type == 'policy', so this is enough to drive a fully
  branded policy page off the merchant's existing admin content.
{% endcomment %}

